msgid "# Netloader Guide"
msgstr "# Netloader 指南"

msgid ""
"This guide provides instructions for using **Netloader** as a weight-loader "
"plugin for acceleration in **vLLM Ascend**."
msgstr "本指南介绍如何在 **vLLM Ascend** 中使用 **Netloader** 作为权重加载插件以加速。"

msgid "## Usage"
msgstr "## 使用方法"

msgid ""
"To enable Netloader, pass `--load-format=netloader` and provide "
"configuration via `--model-loader-extra-config` (as a JSON string). Below "
"are the supported configuration fields:"
msgstr ""
"要启用 Netloader，请传递 `--load-format=netloader` 并通过 `--model-loader-extra-"
"config`（以 JSON 字符串形式）提供配置。以下是支持的配置字段："

msgid ""
"| Field Name         | Type    | Description                                                                                          | Allowed Values / Notes                                                                                       |\n"
"|--------------------|---------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| **SOURCE**         | List    | Weight data sources. Each item is a map with `device_id` and `sources`, specifying the rank and its endpoints (IP:port). <br>Example: `{\"SOURCE\": [{\"device_id\": 0, \"sources\": [\"10.170.22.152:19374\"]}, {\"device_id\": 1, \"sources\": [\"10.170.22.152:11228\"]}]}` <br>If omitted or empty, fallback to default loader. The SOURCE here is second priority. | A list of objects with keys `device_id: int` and `sources: List[str]` |\n"
"| **MODEL**           | String  | The model name, used to verify consistency between client and server.                                | Defaults to the `--model` argument if not specified.                                                         |\n"
"| **LISTEN_PORT**     | Integer | Base port for the server listener.                                                                   | The actual port = `LISTEN_PORT + RANK`. If omitted, a random valid port is chosen. Valid range: 1024–65535. If out of range, that server instance won’t open a listener. |\n"
"| **INT8_CACHE**      | String  | Behavior for handling int8 parameters in quantized models.                                           | One of `[\"hbm\", \"dram\", \"no\"]`. <br> - `hbm`: copy original int8 parameters to high-bandwidth memory (HBM) (may cost a lot of HBM). <br> - `dram`: copy to DRAM. <br> - `no`: no special handling (may lead to divergence or unpredictable behavior). Default: `\"no\"`. |\n"
"| **INT8_CACHE_NAME** | List    | Names of parameters to which `INT8_CACHE` is applied (i.e. filtering).                               | Default: `None` (means no filtering—all parameters).                                                         |\n"
"| **OUTPUT_PREFIX**   | String  | Prefix for writing per-rank listener address/port files in server mode.                              | If set, each rank writes to `{OUTPUT_PREFIX}{RANK}.txt` (text), content = `IP:Port`.                         |\n"
"| **CONFIG_FILE**     | String  | Path to a JSON file specifying the above configuration.                                              | If provided, the SOURCE inside this file has **first priority** (overrides SOURCE in other configs).          |"
msgstr ""
"| 字段名            | 类型    | 描述                                                                                                | 允许值/说明                                                                                                 |\n"
"|--------------------|---------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| **SOURCE**         | 列表    | 权重数据源。每个元素是一个包含 `device_id` 和 `sources` 的映射，指定 rank 及其端点（IP:port）。<br>示例：`{\"SOURCE\": [{\"device_id\": 0, \"sources\": [\"10.170.22.152:19374\"]}, {\"device_id\": 1, \"sources\": [\"10.170.22.152:11228\"]}]}` <br>如果省略或为空，则回退到默认加载器。此处的 SOURCE 为第二优先级。 | 包含键 `device_id: int` 和 `sources: List[str]` 的对象列表 |\n"
"| **MODEL**           | 字符串  | 模型名称，用于验证客户端和服务器之间的一致性。                                                      | 如果未指定，默认为 `--model` 参数。                                                                         |\n"
"| **LISTEN_PORT**     | 整数    | 服务器监听器的基端口。                                                                              | 实际端口 = `LISTEN_PORT + RANK`。如果省略，则随机选择一个有效端口。有效范围：1024–65535。如果超出范围，该服务器实例将不会打开监听器。 |\n"
"| **INT8_CACHE**      | 字符串  | 量化模型中处理 int8 参数的行为。                                                                    | 可选值：`[\"hbm\", \"dram\", \"no\"]`。<br> - `hbm`：将原始 int8 参数复制到高带宽内存（HBM）（可能消耗大量 HBM）。<br> - `dram`：复制到 DRAM。<br> - `no`：不进行特殊处理（可能导致发散或不可预测行为）。默认值：`\"no\"`。 |\n"
"| **INT8_CACHE_NAME** | 列表    | 应用 `INT8_CACHE` 的参数名称（即过滤）。                                                            | 默认值：`None`（表示不过滤——所有参数）。                                                                     |\n"
"| **OUTPUT_PREFIX**   | 字符串  | 在服务器模式下，为每个 rank 写入监听地址/端口文件的前缀。                                          | 如果设置，每个 rank 将写入 `{OUTPUT_PREFIX}{RANK}.txt`（文本），内容为 `IP:Port`。                         |\n"
"| **CONFIG_FILE**     | 字符串  | 指定上述配置的 JSON 文件路径。                                                                      | 如果提供，此文件中的 SOURCE 具有**第一优先级**（覆盖其他配置中的 SOURCE）。                                  |"

msgid "## Example Commands & Placeholders"
msgstr "## 示例命令与占位符"

msgid "> Replace parts in `` `<...>` `` before running."
msgstr "> 运行前请替换 `` `<...>` `` 中的内容。"

msgid "### Server"
msgstr "### 服务器端"

msgid "### Client"
msgstr "### 客户端"

msgid "#### Placeholder Descriptions"
msgstr "#### 占位符说明"

msgid ""
"- `<model_file>`: Path to the model file  \n"
"- `<model_name>`: Model name (must match between server & client)  \n"
"- `<port>`: Base listening port on server  \n"
"- `<server_IP>` + `<server_Port>`: IP and port of the Netloader server (from server log)  \n"
"- `<device_id_diff_from_server>`: Client device ID (must differ from server’s)  \n"
"- `<client_port>`: Port on which client listens"
msgstr ""
"- `<model_file>`：模型文件路径  \n"
"- `<model_name>`：模型名称（服务器和客户端必须一致）  \n"
"- `<port>`：服务器上的基础监听端口  \n"
"- `<server_IP>` + `<server_Port>`：Netloader 服务器的 IP 和端口（来自服务器日志）  \n"
"- `<device_id_diff_from_server>`：客户端设备 ID（必须与服务器不同）  \n"
"- `<client_port>`：客户端监听的端口"

msgid ""
"After startup, you can test consistency by issuing inference requests with "
"temperature = 0 and comparing outputs."
msgstr "启动后，您可以通过发送 temperature = 0 的推理请求并比较输出来测试一致性。"

msgid "## Note & Caveats"
msgstr "## 注意事项"

msgid ""
"- If Netloader is used, **each worker process** must bind a listening port. That port may be user-specified or assigned randomly. If user-specified, ensure it is available.  \n"
"- Netloader requires extra on-chip memory to establish HCCL connections (i.e. `HCCL_BUFFERSIZE`, default ~200 MB). Users should reserve sufficient capacity (e.g. via `--gpu-memory-utilization`).  \n"
"- It is recommended to set `VLLM_SLEEP_WHEN_IDLE=1` to mitigate unstable or slow connections/transmissions. Related info: [vLLM Issue #16660](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/16660), [vLLM PR #16226](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/16226)."
msgstr ""
"- 如果使用 Netloader，**每个工作进程**必须绑定一个监听端口。该端口可由用户指定或随机分配。如果由用户指定，请确保其可用。  \n"
"- Netloader 需要额外的片上内存来建立 HCCL 连接（即 `HCCL_BUFFERSIZE`，默认约 200 MB）。用户应预留足够的容量（例如通过 `--gpu-memory-utilization`）。  \n"
"- 建议设置 `VLLM_SLEEP_WHEN_IDLE=1` 以缓解连接/传输不稳定或缓慢的问题。相关信息：[vLLM Issue #16660](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/16660)，[vLLM PR #16226](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/pull/16226)。"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Netloader leverages high-bandwidth peer-to-peer (P2P) transfers between NPU "
"cards to load model weights. It is implemented as a plugin (via the "
"`register_model_loader` API added in vLLM 0.10). The workflow is:"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"1. A **server** preloads a model.  \n"
"2. A new **client** instance requests weight transfer.  \n"
"3. After validating that the model and partitioning match, the client uses HCCL collective communication (send/recv) to receive weights in the same order as stored in the model."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The server runs alongside normal inference tasks via sub-threads and via "
"`stateless_init_torch_distributed_process_group` in vLLM. The client thus "
"takes over weight initialization without needing to load from storage."
msgstr ""

